com.storytron.swat

Class Swat.EventInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • com.storytron.swat.Swat.EventInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    Swat

    public static class Swat.EventInfo
extends java.awt.Component
    This is a class to share information in the event system. Controls in the aplication can set the source of an event to an instance of this class. Then an AWTEventPostprocessor will know what to do with it, like the want we implemented in Swat.Swat().
